latestPosts.caption:
37th National Games in Goa, how fortunate and honoured i felt to be a part of this games and to represent my state Goa🥳, This experience has raised my floor to an unimaginable height with getting to participate along with accomplished players in Asian games and other elite tournaments. 🥋📈

All Glory and honour to God who blessed me with this opportunity and graced me to accomplish it✨ and my parents and my brother @steve._af for their belief and trust in me 💖

 Thanks to all the coaches and grand master who worked hard to get the best out of me 💪 and it wouldn't be complete without the support and encouragement from all the Teakwondo athletes and specially my roommates who held their shoulder for my happy and sad moments.

Last but not the least my profound thanks to the man behind it all, for his endless support, coaching, care and love. My coach Mr. Siraj Khan♥️ @dedication_personality who's a jewel of a sportsmanship💯

#teakwondo #37thnationalgames #getsetgoa #poomsaechampion
